T02D2765:141b-1: rje chen po mchod sbyin gyi dbang po la phyag 'tshal lo //

T02D2765:141b-4: zhes 'byung ba'i sgrub thabs bshad par bya'o //
T02D2765:141b-5: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dpal nyid //
T02D2765:141b-6: gtsor bcas sangs rgyas sras bcas la //

T02D2765:141b-8: snying rje chen pos gtor ma sbyin //
T02D2765:141b-9: bdag nyid lha yi rnal 'byor pas //

T02D2765:141b-34: na sarba p'u dza me gha sa mu dra spha

T02D2765:141b-48: sarba gardza pa ri pu dyam /
